install office 365 2024
1- Create Config file
2- Download Office Deployment Tool 
 https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=49117
3- mkdir c:\office
4- run the tool and make extrack the setup to c:\office
5- config file to c:\office
6- run powershell :  cd c:\office -> .\setup.exe /configure config.xml
